You would remember me, no?

57
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,203
卡拉奇!
Karachi!

58
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,319
耶思敏被发现了 我们得行动了 埃克斯!
Yasmin's been compromised. We need to move now, Axel!

59
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:59,199
除非我们确定箱子里是什么
No one moves on the Albino

60
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:02,399
否则就不能对付阿尔拜诺 快点
until we have cleared what's in the box. Come on.

61
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:06,519
没错 就是了 我们去年四月在卡拉奇才见过的
Yeah, yeah, yeah. We met in Karachi last April exactly.

62
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:09,719
不过那时候 你可是个酒吧的服务生
But then you were working as a cocktail waitress

63
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:12,241
我没记错吧?
if I remember it correctly?

64
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:20,479
- 他妈的  - 确认了
- Oh, shit. - We got confirmation.

65
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,886
