Boss.

67
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:31,008
撤退
Abort.

68
00:06:48,370 --> 00:06:50,330
再见啦 亲爱的

69
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:01,599
- 喂  - 宝贝 我是爸爸
- Hey.  - Hi sweetie, it's your father.

70
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:04,559
你竟然没忘了我生日 看来说不定你还挺爱我
You didn't forget, which means you probably love me.

71
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,959
我当然爱你了 佐伊
Of course I do, Zooey.

72
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:09,919
大声唱"生日快乐"给我听 我就相信你
You can prove it by singing me "Happy Birthday, " loudly.

73
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:14,199
唔 我很乐意给你唱 但我正在工作
Well, I could sweetheart, but, uh, I'm at work.

74
