我的东西呢?
Where's all my stuff?

131
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:09,879
我还在动手刷房子
I also started to paint the room.

132
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:12,159
我媳妇觉得 这房子最好颜色再亮点
My wife think it is best to have a cheerful color.

133
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:15,759
你喜欢黄色吗? 别担心 伊桑 我挺乐意刷房子的 小菜一碟
Is yellow good for you? I'm happy to do the work. It's not a problem, Ethan.

134
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:18,566
事实上 这麻烦大了 朱尔
Actually, Jules, there is a problem.

135
00:15:22,730 --> 00:15:24,350
除非到了四月十三号

136
