01:45:31,160 --> 01:45:32,521
你病了 伊桑
You're sick, Ethan.

1179
01:45:40,600 --> 01:45:43,679
哇哦 美轮美奂啊
Wow, this is unbelievable.

1180
01:45:43,680 --> 01:45:45,928
是啊 真是太棒了
Yeah. I know. It's crazy.

1181
01:45:55,760 --> 01:45:57,405
我想吐
I'm gonna be sick.

1182
01:45:58,200 --> 01:45:59,970
过来
Come with me.

1183
01:46:17,240 --> 01:46:19,090
你划伤自己了吗?
Did you scratch yourself?

1184
01:46:23,160 --> 01:46:24,799
别去 别去 和我回家
No, please don't go. Come home with me.

1185
01:46:24,800 --> 01:46:26,200
工作让别人去干吧
Just leave it to someone else.

1186
01:46:27,920 --> 01:46:30,122
待在这
Just please stay here.

1187
01:46:43,280 --> 01:46:44,639
- 佐伊!  - 什么?
- Zooey!  - What?

1188
01:46:44,640 --> 01:46:45,966
趴下!
Get down!

1189
01:47:16,480 --> 01:47:18,250
你在里面听得到吗?
You hear me in there?

1190
01:47:19,360 --> 01:47:21,085
我送你下地狱吧
I'm sending you down.

1191
01:48:18,620 --> 01:48:19,865
他死了

1192
01:48:32,960 --> 01:48:34,605
该死
Oh, shit.

1193
01:48:43,160 --> 01:48:44,441
风水轮流转
Wheel's turning.

1194
01:48:48,440 --> 01:48:50,759
别走啊 胆小鬼!
No, stay, you fuckers!

1195
01:48:50,760 --> 01:48:52,883
别走!
Don't!

1196
01:49:06,880 --> 01:49:08,889
我要...
I gotta...

1197
01:49:09,600 --> 01:49:11,484
停下
Don't.

1198
01:49:12,200 --> 01:49:14,084
我不介意杀了你
I wouldn't mind killing you.

1199
01:49:16,800 --> 01:49:19,002
你吓到了很多人
You scared a lot of people up there.

1200
01:49:21,680 --> 01:49:23,848
这是我女儿的派对
This is my daughter's party.

1201
01:49:35,080 --> 01:49:36,611
好的
Yes.

1202
01:49:40,600 --> 01:49:41,687
好的 加油
Yes, come on.

1203
01:49:54,920 --> 01:49:56,406
薇薇
Viv.

1204
01:49:59,000 --> 01:50:01,009
天啊
Oh, my God.

1205
01:50:04,040 --> 01:50:06,479
我在地狱吗?
Am I in hell?

1206
01:50:06,480 --> 01:50:09,639
我的裙底就那么可怕吗 伊桑
So that's what it looks like to you, Ethan.

1207
01:50:09,640 --> 01:50:13,003
早就猜到了
Figures.

1208
01:50:14,640 --> 01:50:17,605
- 干掉他  - 什么?
- Finish it. - What?

1209
01:50:20,080 --> 01:50:22,559
按我的话做
You'll do what I tell you to.

1210
01:50:22,560 --> 01:50:25,969
- 不  - 干掉他
- No.  - Finish it.

1211
01:50:26,680 --> 01:50:29,690
我已经完成我的任务配额了
I passed my quota, Vivi.

1212
01:50:30,680 --> 01:50:31,839
伊桑...
Ethan...

1213
01:50:31,840 --> 01:50:35,089
天啊!
Jesus Christ!

1214
01:50:42,840 --> 01:50:45,486
你真的不再为他们工作了吗?
Are you really done working for them?

1215
01:50:45,880 --> 01:50:48,679
一日杀手终生杀手 他不会改变的
A killer is a killer. He'll never change.

1216
01:50:48,680 --> 01:50:50,639
我知道我这样对你和佐伊不公平
I know I haven't done right by you and Zooey.

1217
01:50:50,640 --> 01:50:52,559
杀了他
Kill him.

1218
01:50:52,560 --> 01:50:54,119
很久之前我就该离开了
I should've left a long time ago.

1219
01:50:54,120 --> 01:50:56,399
- 你女儿出生的时候呢?  - 我没在
- What about your daughter?  - I wasn't there.

1220
01:50:56,400 --> 01:50:59,126
动手
Do it.

1221
01:51:01,120 --> 01:51:03,879
什么样的孩子连车都不会骑?
What kind of kid doesn't know how to ride a bike?

1222
01:51:03,880 --> 01:51:06,651
没爹教的孩子
The kind of kid who never had a father to teach her.

1223
01:51:08,760 --> 01:51:09,961
- 伊桑  - 伊桑!
- Ethan.  - Ethan!

1224
01:51:11,280 --> 01:51:12,599
动手!
Do it!

1225
01:51:12,600 --> 01:51:14,520
保证不再对我撒谎
Promise you'll never lie to me again.

1226
01:51:15,360 --> 01:51:16,641
你没有选择
You have no choice.

1227
01:51:19,520 --> 01:51:21,643
我不认为
I don't think so.

1228
01:51:24,320 --> 01:51:28,047
我妻子想要我金盆洗手了
The wife wants me to give it up.

1229
01:52:07,360 --> 01:52:08,759
我能和她说会话吗?
Can I talk to her?

1230
01:52:08,760 --> 01:52:11,719
不行 她现在在下面的沙滩上扔石子
No, she's down on the beach right now throwing rocks.

1231
01:52:11,720 --> 01:52:14,279
- 什么?  - 嗯 我们在
- What?  - Yeah, we're...

1232
01:52:14,280 --> 01:52:16,119
我们现在正处于调和期
We're taking a break from each other right now.

1233
01:52:16,120 --> 01:52:18,319
至少她不会拿石头扔我了
At least she's not throwing them at me.

1234
01:52:18,320 --> 01:52:20,559
一切还好吗?
Is everything all right?

1235
01:52:20,560 --> 01:52:24,839
都还好 我们的关系好好坏坏
Yeah, it's been all right. There's been good and bad days.

1236
01:52:24,840 --> 01:52:27,079
我们都说了心声
She said things, I've said things.

1237
01:52:27,080 --> 01:52:29,639
虽然有时会有泪水
There's been some tears,

1238
01:52:29,640 --> 01:52:31,922
但这个星期真的很不错
but the week overall's been really worth it.

1239
01:53:05,240 --> 01:53:06,441
嗨
Hey.

1240
01:53:07,680 --> 01:53:10,079
这是我的一些礼物还有 嗯...
These are some presents from me and, um...

1241
01:53:10,080 --> 01:53:12,399
送到家里的一个包裹
a package that was dropped at the house.

1242
01:53:12,400 --> 01:53:15,490
我听到你车子还发动着 你要回去了吗?
I can hear your car running. Are you gonna go back?

1243
01:53:21,240 --> 01:53:23,204
我爱你 蒂娜
I love you, Tina.

1244
01:53:25,520 --> 01:53:27,529
你只是说说而已
Just not enough to quit.

1245
01:53:28,360 --> 01:53:31,962
我想你错了 但是我理解
I think you're wrong, but I understand.

1246
01:53:34,480 --> 01:53:40,159
如果我说一个字能够让你改变主意
If I could say one word to you to change your mind,

1247
01:53:40,160 --> 01:53:42,359
你会给我这个机会吗?
would you give me that chance?

1248
01:53:42,360 --> 01:53:44,005
我们不是在玩游戏
This isn't a game.

1249
01:53:45,160 --> 01:53:47,959
我不奢求和你住在一起 不奢求和你睡在一起
We don't have to stay in the same room, we don't have to sleep together,

1250
01:53:47,960 --> 01:53:50,119
我并不是想问这些
that's not what I'm asking.

1251
01:53:50,120 --> 01:53:53,799
如果这些事必须有个决断 决定权都在你
If that becomes important, you'll be the one to decide.

1252
01:53:53,800 --> 01:53:55,639
只要听到那个音乐 我就知道你们还需要我
I'll hear the music, and then I'll know.

1253
01:53:55,640 --> 01:53:57,490
如果再也听不到了...
And if I never hear it...

1254
01:53:58,920 --> 01:54:01,122
我得到的已经比我应得的要多了
I've already gotten more than I deserve.

1255
01:54:03,640 --> 01:54:08,926
我只是想和妻子女儿待在一起 越久越好
I just wanna hang out as long as I can with my daughter and my wife.

1256
01:54:10,840 --> 01:54:13,799
- 是什么词?  - 什么?
- What's the word?  - What?

1257
01:54:13,800 --> 01:54:15,479
你想用哪个字改变我的主意?
What's the one word to make me change my mind?

1258
01:54:15,480 --> 01:54:19,765
是 呃... 是"圣诞"
It's, uh... it's Christmas.

1259
01:54:22,440 --> 01:54:24,319
那是两个字 伊桑
That's two, Ethan.

1260
01:54:24,320 --> 01:54:26,759
- 嗨 妈妈!  - 嗨 亲爱的
- Hey, Mom!  - Hi, sweetie.

1261
01:54:26,760 --> 01:54:28,200
真高兴你能来!
I'm so glad you came!

1262
01:54:31,480 --> 01:54:33,205
快点 我们进屋去
Come on, let's go inside.

1263
01:54:34,120 --> 01:54:36,049
爸爸会给我们做热巧克力
Dad's gonna make us hot cocoa.

1264
01:54:40,760 --> 01:54:42,041
快点啦
Come on.

1265
01:55:03,040 --> 01:55:04,651
爸爸是坏蛋吗?
Is Dad a badass?

1266
01:55:06,440 --> 01:55:10,486
嗯 他是... 他干的一些事挺混蛋的
Well, he's, um... He's done some things.

1267
01:55:15,840 --> 01:55:19,399
你觉得爸爸会留在这吗?
You think Dad's gonna stick around?

1268
01:55:19,400 --> 01:55:21,125
他会尽量待在这吧 亲爱的
As long as he can, sweetheart.

1269
01:55:23,400 --> 01:55:25,250
他真的很爱你
He loves you so much.

1270
01:55:40,400 --> 01:55:43,250
圣诞快乐 亲爱的!


